  &lt;p&gt;Jets give a closer look a tactile receptors.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ruffini corpuscle are sensing skin stretch.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Meissner respond to light touch and virbation around 50Hz
Pacinain corpuscle will detect rapid 200-300Hz vibration&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Merkel disc detect pressure.&lt;/p&gt;

