&lt;h2 id=&#34;two-point-discrimination&#34;&gt;Two-point discrimination&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Do we have the same tactile sensitivity everywhere?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;aside class=&#34;notes&#34;&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;Mow, do you think we have the same tactile sensitivity everywhere&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2dp 1mm in the tongue&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3 to 8 on the finger&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;36 to 75mm on the back&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It&amp;rsquo;s optimisation of the ressources, we don&amp;rsquo;t need more informations from the back, but we use our hand to grab stuff.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Why optimise&lt;/p&gt;

